Zinzino Health and Wellness Overview followed by Partner Training
Come and learn about the products that are leading the way in Preventative Personalised Test validated Nutrition.

Guests: FREE of Charge

Training on how you can build a solid business alongside these unique products from Ambassador Dave Ives from the UK, Black Crown Kirsten Pearse from Netherlands and Director Sue Booth from the UK.
Book your Partner tickets and Guest tickets at https://shorturl.at/nzBR3

eventDetails:
Join us for a pleasant excursion on the east side! We will walk under the N11 and take the trails and paths through this old forest. Our goal is the newly refurbished Octagon - last seen behind fencing. We should be able to admire the flooring and form an opinion, now that works are complete.
Expect some slope, some slop, and plenty of great views. A post hike lunch in the lovely Grove Bar might be on the cards too....! Please note - there is a charge of €10 per hike and I can supply poles to anyone who would like to borrow them.
